last_episode_to_air.name: Music / Alone
last_episode_to_air.overview: Toad sets out to pair Frog with the ideal instrument. Frog leaves a note that stirs up a flurry of feelings for Toad.

name: Frog and Toad
overview: Frog and Toad are not at all alike. Frog likes new adventures. Toad likes the comforts of home. Yet despite their differences, Frog and Toad are always there for each other—as best friends should be.

episodes.name: Cookies / The Letter
episodes.overview: Frog and Toad try to resist a batch of yummy cookies. Frog finds out Toad has never gotten mail before, so he writes Toad a letter.

episodes.name: Ice Cream / A Lost Button
episodes.overview: Toad's delivery of refreshing ice cream to Frog turns into a melty disaster. Frog and Toad go to great lengths to find a button.

episodes.name: Spring / Dragons and Giants
episodes.overview: Frog wants Toad to spend the first day of spring with him. To prove they're brave, Frog and Toad set off to climb Mount Gloom.

episodes.name: The Garden / A Cake
episodes.overview: Toad thinks the seeds in his new garden are afraid to grow. Frog wants to bake a cake for Toad, even though he doesn't know how.

episodes.name: The Kite / Lost
episodes.overview: Frog and Toad attempt to fly their homemade kite despite some doubting Robins. Frog handles being lost differently than Toad does.

episodes.name: The Story / A List
episodes.overview: Toad goes on an epic quest to find a story to tell an unwell Frog. When Toad loses his to-do list, he's stumped about what to do next.

episodes.name: New Shoes / A Night Out
episodes.overview: Toad is excited about his new shoes—until they cause nothing but trouble. Frog aims to rescue Toad's fancy jacket from a lonely closet.

episodes.name: Waking Up / The Squash
episodes.overview: After a long night's sleep, Toad realizes Frog's been busy without him. Frog helps Toad feel OK about plans not going perfectly.

episodes.name: Christmas Eve
episodes.overview: Frog gets sidetracked while running a last-minute errand on Christmas Eve, causing Toad to wonder about where his friend could be.

episodes.name: Frog and Toad and Stick / Spring Cleaning
episodes.overview: Toad feels left out when Frog gives all his attention to his amazing, most perfect stick. Frog helps Toad tidy up.

episodes.name: The Present / Down the Hill
episodes.overview: Toad struggles to find a gift fit for a fancy box. Frog gives Toad the courage to go sledding.

episodes.name: A Swim / The Surprise
episodes.overview: Frog reassures a swimsuit-shy Toad that he doesn’t look funny at all. Frog and Toad secretly plan to surprise each other.

episodes.name: Tomorrow / The Hat
episodes.overview: Thoughts of chores piling up make it hard for Toad to relax. Frog’s birthday gift for Toad goes over well except for a “small” issue.

episodes.name: The Corner / The Amazing Toad
episodes.overview: Frog and Toad set off on a search for spring. Toad steps in as a last-minute performer but runs into trouble when he can’t see Frog.

episodes.name: Night Calls / Shivers
episodes.overview: Frog convinces Toad to go camping, but the forest creates quite the disturbance. Frog hopes his spooky story gets a reaction from Toad.

episodes.name: The Umbrella / A Vacation
episodes.overview: Frog and Toad try to reunite a lost umbrella with its owner. Vacation plans hit a snag when Toad worries about what to pack.

episodes.name: Stargazing / The Flood
episodes.overview: A picnic dinner stretches well past bedtime for a celestial sighting. Toad comes to the rescue after Frog’s roof springs a leak.

episodes.name: Music / Alone
episodes.overview: Toad sets out to pair Frog with the ideal instrument. Frog leaves a note that stirs up a flurry of feelings for Toad.
